Package ohos.utils

Class Pair<F,S>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.utils.Pair<F,S>

  • public class Pair<F,S>
extends Object
    Provides a data container that saves any two objects as one object.

    By packing two parameters into one, Pair container makes parameter transfer easier.

    1
